Second fpsb release :)

Not much to say about it- you may find a few of the entities are illusionary.
I've tried mucking about with the entity type but I just can't find the right type to make them solid, oh well.
The screenshots make it look empty, but its not really ^^

Feel free if you want to decompile and add a buyzone for it to be a normal aim map :)

Enjoy- comments & constructive criticism appreciated.
